<Author>tlbkwb
<Content>Terrific for Families Fabulous location, easy, quick walk to the U-Bahn station; even quicker to Wurtenburgplatz, with restaurants, ice cream (!), bier garten. KaDaWe department store is right around the corner. Kaiser Wilhelm cathedral within easy walking distance.They were installing the elevator while we were there, and it was almost completed. Difficult to walk up 4 flights, but I managed (knee issues).Room was huge--family of 4 slept very comfortably. Bathroom was tiny, but not a deterrent. Big high ceilings, molding, huge windows. Breakfast was substantial, and the kids loved the scrambled eggs.We were able to check in early (thank you!) as we were exhausted from the train ride. And at checkout, they accommodated our luggage for several hours while we continued to roam about. 
