<Author>JerryO'R
<Content>Peaceful setting Had a great four days at this hotel. No prior knowledge of location or hotel and what a great surprise on both parts when we got there. Great location for eating, U bahn (Wittenberger Platz) and nice walk to S bahn (Zoologischer Garten). Load of shops around: Ka De We (expensive), designer, Nike, Adidas, Wertheim (affordable) and nice eateries (especially 'Paydos' just around corner in Platz from hotel - steak great!).Checked in at 23.30 without any problem. Friendly welcome - better mood than mine. Room on 1st floor very comfortable, spotlessly clean, tea/coffee supplies adequate. Smallish bathroom but ideal for two. Shower lovely and hot. Towels changed daily and room kept very clean. Airconditioning unit very useful. Breakfast plentiful with good coffee. Lovely ambience, especially as the four days we were there the sun never seemed to stop shining. Free use of PC and Wireless network (charge) available.Overall we could not have wished for a nicer and friendlier place to stay and would not hesitate to return. 
