<Author>crawfishbelle
<Content>Spacious room and perfect location The location of this hotel is fantastic! This is the famous shopping area of Berlin with the KaDeWe right next door, so there is plenty to do after the other attractions close for the day. Plus, with a metro stop right outside the hotel, you can easily be anywhere in the city in just a matter of minutes. We were also pleased with the size of the room and that they provided a crib for our baby daughter. Our favorite part was the beautiful breakfast room where we had a relaxing start to every morning. This hotel is the perfect blend of old charm and modern rooms. We were very pleased with our experience and highly recommend this hotel. 
